9. BUSINESS RULES
==================================================
Implement and document these rules:

1. Tracking session can be started only for an eligible rental status
2. Only one active tracking session per rental
3. Location points can only be added to ACTIVE sessions
4. Ending a session prevents further point additions
5. Current location in TrackingSession must always reflect latest point
6. Route history must be ordered by timestamp
7. Geofence checks should evaluate on each new point
8. CITY_ONLY rule can compare tracked point against allowed city metadata in simplified form
9. NO_BORDER_CROSSING can be modeled as warning/placeholder if exact geographic border logic is too heavy
10. The service should be simulation-friendly and not depend on real GPS providers

